15.43	1_(The_Beatles_album)	1 (The Beatles album)	1 is a compilation album by The Beatles, released on 13 November 2000. The album features virtually every number-one single released in the United Kingdom and United States from 1962 to 1970. Issued on the 30th anniversary of the band's break-up, it was their first compilation available on one Compact Disc. 1 was a commercial success, and topped the charts worldwide. The world's best-selling album of the 21st century, 1 has sold over 31 million copies.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/be/The_Beatles_1_album_cover.jpg/220px-The_Beatles_1_album_cover.jpg
